{"tid":901673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【70大壽】查理斯三代同堂全家福 細孫路易笑住影相","createTime":"2018-11-14T07:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T13:00:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"187b22881667c6d3ea0bcdbdcbc5a8919cacd1d0","tid":901673,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:58:27.000Z","msg":"英國皇儲查理斯今天70歲大壽，皇室公開他的官方生日照，難得是首次見他與子孫及新抱大合照，4月才出世的幼孫路易王子也有份。<br />\n照片9月在克拉倫斯宮花園拍攝，身為爺爺的查理斯與妻子卡米拉同坐。長孫佐治坐在他膝上，孫女夏洛特坐在卡米拉身邊，長子威廉王子及其妻凱蒂、次子哈里與身懷六甲的妻子梅根則站在後面，而路易由媽媽凱蒂手抱着。年紀小小的他，對住鏡頭已懂得大展笑顔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181114/large/1542151898_3794.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181114%2Flarge%2F1542151898_3794.jpg&h=bbb8372a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.usmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/royal-family-prince-charles-birthday-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usmagazine.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Froyal-family-prince-charles-birthday-01.jpg&h=b2345266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.newsapi.com.au/image/v1/613940aa7947666ac5c5b9ade4423875\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.newsapi.com.au%2Fimage%2Fv1%2F613940aa7947666ac5c5b9ade4423875&h=f4a7d84d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"565be75d90e75ae0a03dba7d12324f53f9cf30f4","tid":901673,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:13:15.000Z","msg":"右邊兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab3bc9718c4a6ece678ef113e0828399e053c58","tid":901673,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"廢人..."},{"pid":"229b60d2e799b3fa0e62c5e24c2f9fb578a3215e","tid":901673,"uid":38172,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"有件nigga o係度, 影衰哂"},{"pid":"5c6b1bffe424c7